Package com.dataset.service.service.proxy

Class DataSetServiceProxy

java.lang.Object
com.dataset.service.service.proxy.DataSetServiceProxy
public class DataSetServiceProxy extends Object
DataSetServiceProxy is a proxy service for the Dataset service which holds all the validation before performing the actual task in Dataset Service.

    • createRecord

      public RecordCreateResponseVO createRecord(RecordDTO recordDTO, String dataSetName)
      The method createRecord creates a record for a provided data set.
      Parameters:
      recordDTO - This parameter holds the payload of the record that is to be created
      dataSetName - This parameter holds the name of the dataset for which a record is to be created
      Returns:
      RecordCreateResponseVO which contains the id for the created resource followed by success message and dataset name

    • getSortedAndGroupedRecords

      public RecordResponseVO getSortedAndGroupedRecords(String dataSetName, String sortBy, String groupBy, String order)
      Retrieves the records for the specified dataset with optional groupBy or sort By or both operations
      Parameters:
      dataSetName - This parameter holds the dataset name for which sortBy and groupBy operation is to be performed.
      sortBy - This parameter holds the name of the field on which sorting should be done.
      groupBy - This parameter holds the name of the field on which grouping should be done.
      order - This parameter holds the direction of the sort, i.e ASC or DESC
      Returns:
      RecordResponseVO This method returns an object of RecordResponseVO which has some generic fields using which the desired response is populated
